title: Sergei Osipov (footballer, born 1968)
text:
Sergei Vladimirovich Osipov (; born 4 March 1968) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player.
Playing career.
He played 11 seasons in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Rubin-TAN%20Kazan">Rubin-TAN</a>, <a href="FC%20Baltika%20Kaliningrad">FC Baltika Kaliningrad</a>, <a href="FC%20Irtysh%20Omsk">FC Irtysh Omsk</a> and <a href="FC%20Lokomotiv%20Chita">FC Lokomotiv Chita</a>.
